&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Northspyre, the only end-to-end real estate development management platform, empowers developers to make smarter investment decisions with data-driven insights and collaborative workflows. Through automation, analytics, and AI, Northspyre gives teams the real-time information, performance insights, and workflow tools they need to do their job with unparalleled speed and intelligence. By bringing project stakeholders, data, and processes together all on one integrated platform, Northspyre eliminates expensive silos in the development lifecycle, making project delivery simple and outcomes more predictable. Since 2017, Northspyre has been the backbone of operational infrastructure for leading development firms, supporting over $500 billion in projects across the US.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re building the self-driving project for real estate development.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Northspyre is the operating system for real estate development — used by the developers behind billions of dollars of projects across the country. This summer, we&#39;re launching a skunkworks initiative to build the next frontier: autonomous AI agents that can predict, decide, and act across the full lifecycle of a building project. Think of what the self-driving car project was to transportation. That&#39;s the ambition here — applied to how buildings get built.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work directly with the CEO, CTO, and Principal Engineer. Not a team lead. Not a manager&#39;s manager. The three people who decide where the company goes. Your code, your ideas, and your decisions will help shape what Northspyre looks like for the next decade.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Build&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI agents that autonomously monitor, flag, and resolve issues across complex real estate projects — from permitting to procurement to closeout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Agentic workflows that replace hours of human coordination with real-time, context-aware decision loops&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;LLM-powered interfaces that translate messy project data into structured intelligence and actionable insights&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Infrastructure for multi-agent collaboration — agents that hand off tasks, escalate to humans, and learn from outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prototype systems capable of becoming core product features shipped to paying customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is no rubric. We are looking for people, not profiles. That said, the people who will thrive here tend to be:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curious and self-directed — you pursue problems without waiting to be pointed at them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable with ambiguity and able to make good decisions without a complete picture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Systems thinkers — you care about how the pieces fit together, not just your slice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intellectually restless — you go deeper on things that interest you without someone telling you to&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pursuing a BS or MS in Computer Science, Computer Engineering, or related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong CS fundamentals — you can reason about systems, not just write code&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with LLMs, AI agents, or AI/ML pipelines (personal projects count heavily)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working in Python and at least one modern AI/ML framework&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A portfolio or GitHub that shows you&#39;ve built something real — we want to see working projects, not coursework alone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Offer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Base Stipend: $10,000 per month&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Housing Stipend: $5,000 for the summer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full-Time Pipeline: potential for a full time offer for top performers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Program Length: 12 weeks, Summer 2026&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Format: in-person from Ponce City Market in Atlanta, GA&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits and Perks&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;In addition to a competitive salary, we are offering a meaningful stock option package&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Comprehensive Medical, Dental, and Vision. Multiple plan options, including a plan option for 100% employer-paid premium for individual coverage for full-time employees.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;401k Match to help you save for your future (Fully vested after 6 mo eligibility period)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Unlimited Vacation, Paid Sick Leave, and major US Holidays&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Awesome company swag!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Free access to Health Advocate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Hybrid &amp;amp; Remote opportunities - we have an Amazing new office in Midtown Atlanta&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You will be part of a small, professional fast-moving team with minimal supervision&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Annual team gatherings&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Top Three Reasons to Join&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;#1: It’s the Right Time –&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; We’ve already facilitated more than $500 billion of complex projects across the United States&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;#2. Northspyre has the right product –&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; Our technology empowers modern real estate teams to build leveraging data, automation and artificial intelligence to get to faster, more predictable outcomes on complex projects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;#3. Northspyre celebrates a culture of creativity – &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We strive to have a sense of community within Northspyre that encourages diverse viewpoints, openness, and fostering an environment in which employees feel comfortable bringing their whole authentic selves to work.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We know the&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;confidence gap&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;imposter syndrome&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;can get in the way of meeting spectacular candidates, so please don’t hesitate to apply — we’d love to hear from you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
